t": "\u2192\u200eCommercial performance", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ye_(album)"}
{"title_page": "Bougainville bush warbler", "text_new": "{{Speciesbox\n| status = NT\n| status_system = IUCN3.1\n| status_ref = <ref name=\"iucn\">{{cite iucn |authors= |title= '''' |year= 2016|page= |accessdate= }}</ref>\n| genus = Horornis\n| species = haddeni\n| authority = LeCroy & Barker, 2006\n| synonyms = ''Cettia haddeni''\n}}\n\nThe '''Bougainville bush warbler''' or '''odedi''' (''Horornis haddeni'') is a [[bird]] [[species]] initially placed in the \"[[Old World warbler]]\" assemblage, but nowadays moved with its [[Conspecificity|congener]]s to the new cettiid warbler [[family (biology)|family]].\n\nIt was described as [[Bird species new to science|new to science]] in 2006. This bird is only known from the [[Crown Prince Range]] on [[Bougainville Island]] in the [[Solomon Islands]], [[Papua New Guinea]].<ref>{{cite journal |author=Mary LeCroy |author2=F. Keith Barker |last-author-amp=yes |year=2006 |title=A new species of bush-warbler from Bougainville Island and a monophyletic origin for southwest Pacific ''Cettia'' |journal=[[American Museum Novitates]] |volume=3511 |pages=1\u201320 |url=http://digitallibrary.amnh.org/dspace/bitstream/2246/5786/1/N3511.pdf |format=[[Portable Document Format|PDF]] |doi=10.1206/0003-0082(2006)3511[1:ansobf]2.0.co;2}}</ref>\n\nIts status was first evaluated for the [[IUCN Red List]] in 2008, being listed as [[near threatened]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[BirdLife International]] |year=2008 |url=http://www.birdlife.org/action/science/species/global_species_programme/whats_new.html |title=2008 IUCN Redlist status changes |accessdate=May 23, 2008 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080914020126/http://www.birdlife.org/action/science/species/global_species_programme/whats_new.html |archivedate=September 14, 2008 }}</ref><ref>{{cite iucn |author=BirdLife International |author-link=BirdLife International |year=2008 |title=''Cettia haddeni'' |url=https://www.iucnredlist.org/details/22734397/0 |accessdate=January 25, 2011|ref=harv}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Cettiidae}}\n{{Taxonbar|from=Q27075463}}\n\n[[Category:Horornis]]\n[[Category:Birds described in 2006]]\n\n\n{{Cettiidae-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Speciesbox\n| status = NT\n| status_system = IUCN3.1\n| genus = Horornis\n| species = haddeni\n| authority = LeCroy & Barker, 2006\n| synonyms = ''Cettia haddeni''\n}}\n\nThe '''Bougainville bush warbler''' or '''odedi''' (''Horornis haddeni'') is a [[bird]] [[species]] initially placed in the \"[[Old World warbler]]\" assemblage, but nowadays moved with its [[Conspecificity|congener]]s to the new cettiid warbler [[family (biology)|family]].\n\nIt was described as [[Bird species new to science|new to science]] in 2006. This bird is only known from the [[Crown Prince Range]] on [[Bougainville Island]] in the [[Solomon Islands]], [[Papua New Guinea]].<ref>{{cite journal |author=Mary LeCroy |author2=F. Keith Barker |last-author-amp=yes |year=2006 |title=A new species of bush-warbler from Bougainville Island and a monophyletic origin for southwest Pacific ''Cettia'' |journal=[[American Museum Novitates]] |volume=3511 |pages=1\u201320 |url=http://digitallibrary.amnh.org/dspace/bitstream/2246/5786/1/N3511.pdf |format=[[Portable Document Format|PDF]] |doi=10.1206/0003-0082(2006)3511[1:ansobf]2.0.co;2}}</ref>\n\nIts status was first evaluated for the [[IUCN Red List]] in 2008, being listed as [[near threatened]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[BirdLife International]] |year=2008 |url=http://www.birdlife.org/action/science/species/global_species_programme/whats_new.html |title=2008 IUCN Redlist status changes |accessdate=May 23, 2008 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080914020126/http://www.birdlife.org/action/science/species/global_species_programme/whats_new.html |archivedate=September 14, 2008 }}</ref><ref>{{cite iucn |author=BirdLife International |author-link=BirdLife International |year=2008 |title=''Cettia haddeni'' |url=https://www.iucnredlist.org/details/22734397/0 |accessdate=January 25, 2011|ref=harv}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Cettiidae}}\n{{Taxonbar|from=Q27075463}}\n\n[[Category:Horornis]]\n[[Category:Birds described in 2006]]\n\n\n{{Cettiidae-stub}}\n", "name_user": "WolfmanSF", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200etop:clean up", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bougainville_bush_warbler"}
